{
  "stem": "9102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually at that time, being young, you kind of thought it would be-- you know, it was kind of an honor, you know, to be as such.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, that you had to wear a Star of David because you were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember one of my brothers of my mother got married in front of a synagogue, where I have a picture of later on, and there I had to wear the Star of David.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to wear the Star of David to play outside, and all this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that had bad consequences because you had so many kids who really, you know, had it in for you and, you know, gave you a rough time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all kind of-- you know, dirty Jew and all this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, I remember having a ball and, you know, they took it away and there was nothing you could do because, you know, you were not supposed to play.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not-- I was not supposed to be, as Jewish, to go in the parks anymore because that was all-- you know, not allowed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we lived close to a-- to a park, and I couldn't even go in and play in the sandbox, or whatever it was, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were not allowed to go in the park.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you had to stay kind of on the street where everybody could see you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in that-- well, that was basically in 19-- not right away in '40, but '41, '42 it started to become that way.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then in the end of '42, they started the razias, what was basically the pickups for the-- where they started to take care of the Jewish people and pick them up from the street, originally.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
